dct_description_sm: This point data layer represents public schools for Wisconsin in 2014. The dataset was originally published by the Wisconsin Department of Public Instruction in 2014. [This dataset includes point location data for public schools in Wisconsin. The points are placed on or near each school building's centroid.]
